    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
参上仕候よし<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">被<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">二</seg>仰聞<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">一</seg></seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（おほせきかされ）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>候。然ニ私方にも唯今長府馬関<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">在番其</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">赤馬関奉行</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>余両人計参居申候。<seg rend="warichu" rendition="span">（但シ昨夜出崎仕候由也。）</seg><lb />
商会に取組の<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb"><seg facs="../../../gaiji/1-02/1-02-24.png" rend="gaiji" rendition="img" source="※(コト、1-2-24)" /></seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（こと）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>共次第此度は取定度との事なり。<lb />
何か御かまい無<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>之事なれバ、御手書たまハり度、先上件申上候。謹言。<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">則報<seg rend="chitsuki_1" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 1em">龍</seg></seg>
